## 為什麼用 Firestore
- ⚡ 即時同步（多裝置自動同步）
- 🔐 內建 Auth（Google / FB / Email / SMS）
- 📦 Storage、Functions、Hosting
- 💰 免費額度大（50k reads/day）
- 🚀 React Native / Flutter 親密

## 缺點
- Vendor lock-in（Google）
- 複雜查詢限制多
- 計費複雜（讀寫都算錢）
- 沒有真 JOIN
- 不是標準 SQL

## 初始化
```javascript
// npm install firebase
import { initializeApp } from "firebase/app";
import { getFirestore } from "firebase/firestore";

const app = initializeApp({
  apiKey: "...",
  projectId: "...",
});

const db = getFirestore(app);
```

## CRUD

### Create
```javascript
import { collection, addDoc, setDoc, doc } from "firebase/firestore";

// 自動 ID
const ref = await addDoc(collection(db, "users"), {
  name: "Alice",
  age: 25,
  createdAt: new Date()
});

// 指定 ID
await setDoc(doc(db, "users", "user-1"), {
  name: "Alice"
});
```

### Read
```javascript
import { getDoc, getDocs, query, where, orderBy, limit } from "firebase/firestore";

// 單筆
const snap = await getDoc(doc(db, "users", "user-1"));
const data = snap.data();

// 多筆
const q = query(
  collection(db, "users"),
  where("age", ">=", 18),
  where("active", "==", true),
  orderBy("createdAt", "desc"),
  limit(20)
);
const snap = await getDocs(q);
snap.forEach(doc => console.log(doc.id, doc.data()));
```

### Update
```javascript
import { updateDoc } from "firebase/firestore";
await updateDoc(doc(db, "users", "user-1"), {
  age: 26
});
```

### Delete
```javascript
import { deleteDoc } from "firebase/firestore";
await deleteDoc(doc(db, "users", "user-1"));
```

## Realtime 訂閱（殺手特色）
```javascript
import { onSnapshot } from "firebase/firestore";

const unsub = onSnapshot(
  query(collection(db, "messages"), orderBy("createdAt", "desc")),
  (snap) => {
    snap.docChanges().forEach(change => {
      console.log(change.type, change.doc.data());
    });
  }
);

// 取消
unsub();
```

## Security Rules（必設）
```javascript
// Firestore Console → Rules
rules_version = '2';
service cloud.firestore {
  match /databases/{database}/documents {

    // users：每人只能改自己
    match /users/{userId} {
      allow read: if request.auth != null;
      allow write: if request.auth.uid == userId;
    }

    // posts：公開讀、登入可寫
    match /posts/{postId} {
      allow read: if true;
      allow write: if request.auth != null;
    }
  }
}
```

⚠️ 預設規則 `allow read, write: if false`—不設規則就完全鎖死。

## 限制
- 單文件 < 1 MB
- 集合查詢 < 500 results / call
- 不能 OR 多欄位（要 array-contains）
- 不能複雜 JOIN

## Firestore vs MongoDB

| 面向 | Firestore | MongoDB |
|---|---|---|
| Hosted | 必須 | 可自架 |
| Realtime | 內建 | 需 Change Streams |
| Auth | 整合 | 自己刻 |
| 查詢 | 限制多 | 強大 |
| 鎖定 | Google lock-in | 可換 |

## 適合場景
- ✅ 行動 App（React Native / Flutter）
- ✅ MVP 快速上線
- ✅ 即時聊天 / 通知
- ❌ 複雜查詢 / 分析
- ❌ 怕 vendor lock-in

